Package: inbreedR
Title: Workflows for analysing Inbreeding and HFCs based on SNP or Microsatellite Markers
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
        "Martin A. Stoffel <martin.adam.stoffel@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
        "Mareike Esser <messer@uni-bielefeld.de> [aut]"))
Description: inbreedR provides functions around the framework of heterozygosity-fitness correlations and inbreeding from both 
             microsatellite and SNP datsets.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
